school_name: New Mexico Institute of Mining and Technology
comments: I expected to learn more about computer modeling and simulation. I felt there were too many small Java programming assignments. He was very lenient on grading, but my final grade was lower than I expected. He never used the textbook.

school_name: New Mexico Institute of Mining and Technology
comments: Expects students to read the textbook every day there is class. At only two and a half weeks into the semester, we are supposed to have read nearly 500 pages of text. While he does try to be helpful, his lectures and instructions are more than lacking.
